channel.description:
[center][img]http://conceptionx.net78.net/img/wog.png[/img][/center] [center][img]http://img197.imageshack.us/img197/188/websiteiconr.png[/img][url=http://conceptionx.org/]Website[/url][/center] [size=14pt][b]Introduction[/b][/size] Here ConceptionX the unique server start. I already did much on it and it does looks realy good. I have added some features like complete player and npc folowing clipping and a small start of the custom maps because there will be much more. I have build up the Website and forums that will be soon available for people. I am getting developers to help me with coding and creativity. The right of all developers are same. so i am not getting some shit and kick you out. This is an serious project. I am in need of some good people. I am keeping all normal all 317 DATA and 377 Items like the normal Pi already have it. That means so no 500+ contents like new anims and other... The cache is 20mb. and i am not going up more then 25mb (Spirits work.). Almost all 317 loading some 600+ data are over 200mb. Right? who would like to download. Maybe. But i want something fast and fun. The project just started and will be continued to the end. Nothing other to say about that. If have any question just feal free to ask. The base is an original Project insanity from the official release. [size=14pt][b]Team[/b][/size] [ul][li]Xion - Head Client developer and Normal Source developer. (Me)[/li] [li]Dylan - Head Source Developer and Normal Client developer.[/li] [li]Other spaces empty[/li][/ul] [b][size=14pt]Media[/size][/b] [IMG]http://img143.imageshack.us/img143/308/12210631.png[/img] [url=http://postimage.org/image/hch9l0v8/][img]http://s2.postimage.org/hch9l0v8/Untitled.jpg[/img][/url] [b][size=14pt]Application form[/size][/b]
